      "text": "いや、送っていくって言ったんだけど……\n全然聞いてないじゃないか。どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I said I’d take you…\nYou’re not listening at all. What’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4162373431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.3491846045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、集中出来てなくて……\n私ってほんとダメダメですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I couldn’t concentrate…\nI’m so useless…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1957707704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……愛？　もしかして、何か悩みがあるのか？\n俺で良ければ聞くけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ai? Is something bothering you?\nYou can talk to me if you want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9902064919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ！　なんでもないんです、本当に\n私は大丈夫ですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! It’s nothing‚ really.\nI’m totally fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9051062296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった、でも何かあったらいつでも頼ってくれ\n打ち合わせ、続けて大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay. But if something’s wrong‚ don’t hesitate to tell me.\nCan we continue the meeting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
